The bundle offers a set of 87 Persian fonts derived from X
Series 2 fonts released by Behnam at Irmug.com. In these fonts
the solid dot shape zero, ARABIC-INDIC DIGIT ZERO (uni0660,
uni066F), is changed to hollow circular zero and the glyphs
with YEH ABOVE is changed to the glyphs with HAMZA ABOVE, e.g.
ARABIC LETTER HEH WITH YEH ABOVE ISOLATED FORM (uniFBA5) has
been changed to ARABIC LETTER HEH WITH HAMZA ABOVE ISOLATED
FORM.
